<h2 class="text-info">SUNRIDGE HOA</h2>
<p>Sunridge Home Owners Association has a current site that was created by
	students for their neighborhood. Although the website works, the board
	members want added functionality.</p>
<p>This is the description quoted from the capstone project by Professory
	Fry at Weber State University:</p>
<p>"A real project for the Sunridge Homeowner's Association - allowing
	administrators to manage their website "word press" style - without
	knowing HTML, and allowing owners to manage their ownership information
	(as well as pay annual dues, access secure documents, post classified
	ads, fill out forms, etc.).""</p>
<p>My team, Visionary Tech, has taken on this project. We have documented
