<h3 class="text-success">What's next?</h3>
<p>Our team needs to have our website work with a database to actually store all
	the information of the residents of Sunridge. There are also other 
	functionalites we are hoping to get to. Below are our User Stories which
	outlines what the Board Members have expressed they would like.</p>
<br />

<p>
<h5>PROFILES</h5>
As an owner, I need to be able to update my contact information, so the board can easily
communicate with me. <br />
As a board member, I need the ability to quickly look up owners - by name, or lot, so I can
contact them in a variety of ways (e-mail, text, phone call)<br />
<br />

<h5>INVOICING</h5>
As a board member, I need to be able to send a bulk invoice with details so that all owners
receive an invoice and know what it’s for.<br />
As a board member, I need to be able to send individual invoices to owners so that they can
see the dues that they owe.<br />
As a board member, I need the ability to mark invoices as paid when I receive a check so that
there is a record of invoices paid. <br />
As an owner, I need to see my current balance of dues owed so that I know what I have paid
and what is still due. <br />
As an owner, I need to be able to pay my dues online for each lot I own so that I don’t have to
mail in a check. <br />
(Need to be sure when payment is made, it indicates which lot has made payment.)<br />
<br />

<h5>COMMUNICATION</h5>
As an owner, I need to be able to easily send a communication to the board so that my
concerns can be addressed<br />
As a board member, I need to be notified when a communication comes in so that I can
respond to them in a timely manner.<br />
As an owner, I need to be able to see communication threads so that I can have a paper trail of
communications with board members.<br />
<br />

<h5>CALENDAR</h5>
As a board member, I need to be able to add events to the calendar quickly so that the
community can stay informed of events.<br />
<br />

<h5>FORMS</h5>
As an owner, I need to be able to fill out forms electronically so that I can request a cabin and
get approval from the board.<br />
<br />

<h5>KEYS</h5>
As an owner, I need to be able to see my keys so that I can know which keys are assigned to
me.<br />
As an owner, I need to be able to report my keys as missing so that the board can know that it
is lost.<br />
As a board member, I need the ability to assign and remove keys on lots so that there is a
record of who has which keys.<br />
<br />

<h5>MOBILE FRIENDLY</h5>
As an owner, I need the website to work on mobile devices so that I can access it when I don’t
have a computer handy.<br />
<br />

<h5>ADMIN</h5>
As a board member, I need the ability to create new accounts for owners, so they can access
the site.<br />
As a board member, I need the ability to assign new owners to existing lots (and retire old
owner accounts).<br />
As a board member, I need the ability to upload multiple documents - either to the public facing
site, a particular owner lot, or a private folder that’s accessible to owners only.<br />
<br />

<h5>Additional Information for consideration:</h5>
1. New tab for ‘Minutes’ instead of ‘Other.’ <br />
2. Create a ‘bounceback’ email to the owner (from the board) acknowledging when
they have submitted a communication to the board.<br />
3. Automated email to communications administrator when a lot owner submits a
communication.<br />
4. Create a ‘New Owner’ tab with important information needed as a new lot owner.<br />
5. Where could we have critical Weber County contact information if a lot owner has
questions.<br />
6. Consider a live web cam on the site.<br />
7. More advanced weather links in addition to the scrolling weather at the bottom of
the page. www.noaa.gov, www.weather.gov, radar.weather.gov. Etc.<br />

</p>